$MUDNAME$ concepts help
crafts

.SH Description:
.SP 5 5
The crafts subskills affect your ability to build, create or repair
certain things in the game.  For instance, crafts.smithing.black.weapons
affects your ability to "fix" weapons, or forge new ones.
To see your current crafting skills, type "skills crafts".
.EP

.SH See Also:
.SI 5
fix, skills.
